{"type": "article", "id": 8001, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考。", "date": "2015-04-01T07:51:07Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 8427, "name": "笔记本保护套"}, {"id": 8428, "name": "凉拖"}, {"id": 2476, "name": "托盘"}, {"id": 8429, "name": "剪刀"}, {"id": 8430, "name": "充电器"}], "category": 17, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 59, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702102357Z6xq3bPJ7nMKDizr.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>\r\n\tBrik Case by Jolt Team \r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t来自旧金山的 Jolt Team 推出了一款自定义笔记本保护套，这款保护套被安装在电脑上之后，可以允许用户在其表面搭建乐高风格的积木图案。既可以保护电脑，又能够充分体现个性。不过，这个作品看起来是乐高风格，却不是仅仅和 LEGO 合作的，Mega Bloks、 PixelBlocks、 KRE-O 和 K’NEX Bricks 都在合作范围内，为消费者提供了更多的选择。目前这款产品正在 Kickstarter 上众筹，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/joltteam/brik-case\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102343WgxwlapYfSIBnZrO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102344J4e0wTvaxo2WSXzA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102344s03fY8GXkKZVbda7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102344AQoT0tdnyhE5lcNz.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;white-space:normal;\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021023452yYZ1R9naUdv7Wrh.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62571429\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tUC 01 by Jasper Morrison\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\tJasper Morrison 设计的这一款充电器意在解决桌面线材凌乱和器材同时充电的问题。目前人们普遍习惯拿 USB 线充电，但是许多电脑的 USB 接口数量有限，这时 UC 01 便可以派上用场了。看起上虽然有点笨笨的，但轻便的设计使得它十分便于携带，并排的插口也让线材看上去不那么凌乱不堪。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021023451Yn9SNbtzomDwqau.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102346zGBhAZ4bUPsuix5S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102346AOaPr09oBveJpqNz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64669927\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102346amiICXP7TZvSY9ql.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102347nseYqUVxhaBp1lQr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73471883\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102347fuhCygnM63wTJpvQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70293399\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102348nkiA59gtYav86Sdz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57212714\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tMATHEMATICS Scissors by iAN Yen\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t设计师 iAN Yen 推出了一款“黄金分割剪刀”，剪刀的外形正好符合黄金分割的比例要求。在视觉上带来享受的同时，剪刀握在手里也十分舒服，剪刀是日常生活中必不可少的用品，但是其设计时常以功能性为主，忽略设计美感。设计师试图以此作品来展现剪刀设计美学发展的可能性。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102348ugxFwLil9RZ06KSr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102349W0nkTpRuNb67PIH1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102349boGEDc6ZMmpiCTnk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021023494xCsRlVcIum5q2th.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102350iTNMdeW8J1qQ5UnO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102350NfEPF4Dt3qpM8uw0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102350pO8cwegEYzUKCM1L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102351uNnqM7AeZIlHLP6j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tModern Times Special Series by Roberu \r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t香港生活概念店舖 Modern Times 店内摆设了一个皮革制的托盘，没想到却频频被人问起是否可以出售，所以设计师 Roberu 将它作为一个特别系列产品推出了。这款托盘有棕色，红色和黑色可选，材料是精致的皮革，底部配有一块幼细毛布使得底盘更加稳定，看上去优雅美丽。目前售价为 680 港币，<a href=\"http://www.moderntimes.hk/#!roberu-for-modern-times-series/chzh\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102351QDAHyvmcGBEd24UV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102352GIJgX6ozVqbyed3k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.00257732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102353BUPST8cVdN7HAhYg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.97953964\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102353kI4hzBNvmV1j9D7e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.00515464\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021023541y8cMgTYKza9SdqR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.98976982\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102354XEeJLCI7cVfgYPvl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67684478\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tAdidas Originals by Jeremy Scott Teddy Bear\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\tJeremy Scott 在继和 Adidas 合作推出运动鞋之后，又在最近发布了一款 Adidas Originals 泰迪熊凉拖。从去年开始，这种非人字形的凉拖就开始火爆，不知道今年这款泰迪熊凉拖会不会引发新一轮风潮呢。目前这款凉拖售价为 70 美元，<a href=\"http://www.oneness287.com/collections/all/products/adidas-jeremy-scott-teddy\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102354GvuNI54MgSpTwhJ9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66538462\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021023554diQ3GTFwvy98gN6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66538462\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021023557NpQErlHIc5f3u2z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66538462\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102355J6MsPRQp3UIz7TNc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66538462\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102356v1VLkrX0iaU8PgHs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66538462\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102356AhES1fgrZuQsOCy7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102357KlH6c2ExW91iIB30.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'sans serif', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;\"></span> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}